==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Toadflax
<hw>Toad"flax`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>An herb (<spn>Linaria vulgaris</spn>) of the Figwort family, having
narrow leaves and showy orange and yellow flowers; -- called also
<altname>butter and eggs</altname>, <altname>flaxweed</altname>, and
<altname>ramsted</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Toadhead</ent>⟦br⟧
